reviewText: I moved to England for 18 months to be with my fianc so maybe my experience there has created a certain understanding of the Brit humor but Micky Flanagan is a comedic genius. His 'cockney geezer' persona touches on such a variety of topics that it is impossible not to relate to him and his stories. You have to watch it, although maybe not in front of the kids as the adult language is there throughout.
